<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Well Done! Puzzle Completed Successfully</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family:
          "Outfit", "Inter", "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.15);
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4ade80 0%, #22c55e 100%);
        padding: 40px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #000000;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .header .sub {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #000000;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .success-icon {
        font-size: 50px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .welcome-text {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #0f172a;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .success-paragraph {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #475569;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .info-container {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .info-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;
      }

      .info-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .info-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #475569;
      }

      .info-value {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      .attention-box {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #0f172a;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding: 15px;
        background: #fffdf5;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid #e2b026;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .footer {
        background: #f8fafc;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #94a3b8;
        font-size: 13px;
        border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      }

      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background: #f1f5f9;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
        <div class="sub">You Completed Today's Crossword</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <div class="success-icon">🎉</div>
        <p class="welcome-text">Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p class="success-paragraph">
          Congratulations! You have successfully solved and submitted your entry
          for today's crossword puzzle. Here are your submission details:
        </p>

        <div class="info-container">
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Puzzle:</span>
            <span class="info-value"><%= puzzleTitle %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Solve Time:</span>
            <span class="info-value"><%= solveTime %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Today's Prize:</span>
            <span class="info-value"><%= prize %></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="attention-box">
          💡 <strong>What's Next?</strong><br />
          Keep an eye on your email inbox! If you are chosen as the daily
          winner, we will send you a congratulations email with instructions on
          how to claim your prize.
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; margin: 0">
          Thank you for playing, and good luck!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Daily Crossword Platform. All
        rights reserved.<br />
        If you did not submit a crossword entry, please ignore this email.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
